content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5319.56 - Door close procedures

State Regulations

When all of a gaming device's external doors are closed, the game shall return to its original state and display an appropriate error
message, until the next game has ended. Notes
